Beat Bobby Flay - Season 1, Episode 5




Beauty and the Feast

Farm girl Rochelle Bilow takes on city boy Paul Denamiel for the ultimate prize, a chance to take on Bobby Flay. Who better to guide them into battle than Cooking Channel's Eden Grinshpan and Food Network Star winner Justin Warner? The competition fires up as these chefs compete to Beat Bobby Flay!




Original Air Date: 27-Mar-2014
